{"tid":1309744,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"失業真係好Q正","createTime":"2019-07-12T10:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T12:57:49.000Z","uid":238801,"like":62,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6bee30fd9f9f5b21b527e3ebd765cf0fee4e02a6","tid":1309744,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:39:07.000Z","msg":"每日起身慢慢食早餐, 睇住旁邊D西裝友趕頭趕命,自己懶懶飲杯奶茶 <br />\n<br />\n食完早餐, 返屋企上網搵工, 每日SEND十封信差唔多, <br />\n<br />\n之後訓覺, 訓到十二點或者一點起身, 可以開電腦睇劇, 睇電影, 打下機, 有左電腦, 呢個世界大把免費娛樂 <br />\n<br />\n到左三四點, 可能會覺肚餓, 由於消耗唔多, 可以考慮落街10蚊兩個包, 或者 食麥皮 <br />\n<br />\nHEA到晚上, 如果有家人就返屋企食飯, 冇就盡可能自己煮, 節省少少 <br />\n<br />\n失業左一個月, 依照咁既生活方式, 扣除必要開支, 總支出大概平時返工四成左右, <br />\n<br />\n諗落都覺得好笑, 我辛苦工作, 為左就係六七十歲後, 可以享受類似咁既休閒寧靜既生活 <br />\n<br />\n原來失業已經可以做到, 人生真係可笑, 哈哈"},{"pid":"e3b43968d54cceea57532918f36d5f3793433fb4","tid":1309744,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:43:04.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45f7f54a086cdfadff7f0026183532e47f30b7f5","tid":1309744,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:44:00.000Z","msg":"樓豬已是人生贏家"},{"pid":"5159a8212546fa9bc5ccd71142c6a3cd5ca1ceb3","tid":1309744,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3b43968d54cceea57532918f36d5f3793433fb4","tid":1309744,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:43:04.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T10:44:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a